text: Maja Veršeć (born 23 October 1916, date of death unknown) was a Croatian gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1916 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Croatian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Zagreb
